<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ر ذ ل:</span> <span class="c2">(الرَّذْلُ)</span> الدُّونُ الْخَسِيسُ وَقَدْ <span class="c2">(رَذُلَ)</span> مِنْ بَابِ ظَرُفَ فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(رَذْلٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(رُذَالٌ)</span> بِالضَّمِّ مِنْ قَوْمٍ <span class="c2">(رُذُولٍ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(أَرْذَالٍ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(رُذَلَاءَ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(أَرْذَلَهُ)</span> غَيْرُهُ وَ <span class="c2">(رَذَلَهُ)</span> أَيْضًا فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(مَرْذُولٌ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(رُذَالُ)</span> كُلِّ شَيْءٍ رَدِيئُهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>